{"tid":1148441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞銀︰港樓再升十年 「大灣區」「新香港人」谷樓價","createTime":"2019-05-10T12:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T10:17:48.000Z","uid":3189,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"95bd8dde8450f82a5fe892e3713792d454e69b32","tid":1148441,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190510/large/1557480355_8a49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190510%2Flarge%2F1557480355_8a49.jpg&h=644c511d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瑞銀集團（UBS）最新發表的樓市預測報告認為，香港樓市將會迎來另一個十年大升市。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n香港樓價早已是全球最難負擔的市場，沒有父幹母幹的話，上車談何容易。瑞銀集團（UBS）最新發表的樓市預測報告，可能會令年輕人感到更絕望，因為瑞銀認為，香港樓市將會迎來另一個十年大升市。<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀樓市分析師John Lam認為，大灣區規劃會為香港帶來外來人口，新香港人的購買力會填補人口老化所造成的住屋需求下降。根據瑞銀的樓市數據顯示，本港樓價已連續三個月上升，反映2018年8月至今年1月的樓市調整，可能只是曇花一現。John Lam估計未來十年，香港每年對樓宇單位需求達6萬個，比較政府4.5萬個的估算還要高。<br />\n<br />\n由於低息環境持續，加上樓宇供應有限，香港樓價近月已持續回升，除了瑞銀，彭博行業研究（Bloomberg Intelligence）房地產分析師Patrick Wong亦曾指，限於供應量少及人口持續上升，他預測2019年香港樓價會有一成的上升空間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190510/59586255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190510%2F59586255&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=63db0c51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190510%2F59586255&h=9600fa81\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190510/59586255</a>"},{"pid":"3780032a96139c4f620c7199050a3bbb129fb0b9","tid":1148441,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:58:29.000Z","msg":"瑞銀：三大因素撐起樓價 港樓或再升十年<br />\n<br />\n中美貿易衝突升溫，環球股市震盪，惟本港樓市交投依然熾熱。繼匯豐及大摩後，再有大行唱好本港樓市。瑞銀(UBS)對本港樓市前景樂觀，雖然本港已是全球樓價最難負擔的城市，但預期在以下三大因素支撐下，樓價難有下跌空間，未來十年仍有機會向上。<br />\n<br />\n1. 大灣區居民對港樓需求大<br />\n<br />\n隨著大灣區進一步發展，香港有望與內地部分城市融合，未來會有更多大灣區的居民來港入市，在大量需求支持下，港樓難有大跌空間。此外，大量新買家湧現，可抵銷本港人口老化導致的住屋需求下降，可延續過去20年樓價升勢。<br />\n<br />\n2.房屋供應量不足<br />\n<br />\n本港房屋供應量持續不足，在供求失衡的情況下，刺激樓價節節向上。瑞銀預計，未來十年本港每年的住房需求將達到6萬戶，遠高於政府每年4.5萬戶的供應目標。<br />\n<br />\n3.低息環境吸引買家入市<br />\n<br />\n持續低息的環境，增加市民置業的慾望，加上供應量不足，更能加快買家入市步伐，從而推高樓價。<br />\n<br />\n在中美貿易矛盾升級的陰霾下，樓價依然懶理外圍局勢，繼續拾級而上。中原公布，中原城市領先指數CCL最新報186.07點，按周升1.17%，已連升13周。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1557485298683&amp;issue=20190510\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantp2.php%3Fnode%3D1557485298683%26issue%3D20190510&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=fed1e21f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantp2.php?node=1557485298683&amp;issue=20190510</a>"},{"pid":"1e9f0670411bd9678256f841ee9a7e38cf8882de","tid":1148441,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"瑞銀料港樓市有十年大運 大灣區利內地居民湧港<br />\n<br />\n過去數月間樓市氣氛逆轉，近月樓價亦已止跌回升，加上新盤市場持續暢旺，整體市況均呈現一片大好形勢。瑞銀指大灣區倡議利好本港樓市，未來十年將續呈升勢， 彭博分析亦料本港樓價今年上漲10%。<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀集團的數據顯示，作為全球樓價最高的香港， 樓價將在未來十年內保持上漲。<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀地產分析師John Lam在一份研究報告中寫道， 大灣區項目將不少中國城市與香港融為一體，內地居民流入將成為關鍵。中國買家可以綽綽有餘地推高本港樓市， 解決因為人口老化導致住房需求減少的問題。<br />\n<br />\n他估計，未來十年住房需求每年將達到6萬個單位，遠高於政府的長期供應目標 ─ 每年為市民供應4.5萬個單位。<br />\n<br />\n另彭博房地產分析師Patrick Wong表示：「樓價可能在短期內會有一些調整，但在未來五到十年將會持續上漲。主要原因是人口不斷增長和土地供應有限。他預計今年樓價將攀升10%。<br />\n<br />\n撰文 : 曾子龍 本網記者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2347843/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E6%96%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8B%20%20%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%88%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%B9%A7%E6%B8%AF?mtc=20038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2347843%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E9%258A%2580%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258B%2520%2520%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%2588%25A9%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25B1%2585%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%25B9%25A7%25E6%25B8%25AF%3Fmtc%3D20038&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=778824bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2347843/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E6%96%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8B%20%20%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%88%A9%E5%85%A7%E5%9C%B0%E5%B1%85%E6%B0%91%E6%B9%A7%E6%B8%AF?mtc=20038</a>"},{"pid":"dcc71cfc63288398aeefdff3cba378afe4af57a6","tid":1148441,"uid":56147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T12:59:39.000Z","msg":"以前都敢出下名<br />\n<br />\n而家真係純尻up.. 下次搵peter chan黎講"},{"pid":"cff19dd55de9c9f83f71ba8c24c17fc35c9cffef","tid":1148441,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"瑞銀看好港樓市 料再漲十年<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀(UBS)對本港樓市前景看法樂觀，認為樓價還會再上漲10年。<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀發表研究報告指出，隨着大灣區項目將中國內地一些城市與香港融為一體，居民的流入將成為關鍵。新湧入的買家將足以抵消本港人口老齡化而導致的住房需求下跌。這將延續香港樓價過去20年的上漲趨勢。<br />\n<br />\n瑞銀估計，未來10年，本港每年的住房需求將達到6萬戶，遠高於政府每年4.5萬戶的長期供應目標。<br />\n<br />\n另外，外電引述房地產分析師表示，由於人口增長和土地供應有限，香港樓價可能會有一些短期調整，但未來5至10年會繼續上漲，預計今年本港樓價將有一成的升幅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2134607/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82+%E6%96%99%E5%86%8D%E6%BC%B2%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fhongkong%2Farticle%2F2134607%2F%25E7%2591%259E%25E9%258A%2580%25E7%259C%258B%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2B%25E6%2596%2599%25E5%2586%258D%25E6%25BC%25B2%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=7651a176\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/hongkong/article/2134607/%E7%91%9E%E9%8A%80%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E6%B8%AF%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82+%E6%96%99%E5%86%8D%E6%BC%B2%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4</a>"},{"pid":"f670e05d3f51157e8c40407f8f3bdd2f260fa478","tid":1148441,"uid":103981,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"大灣區咁撚大，點解個個都要迫黎香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陷家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8576395d8997c77774bae1c4f3a58669103c756","tid":1148441,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"樓市gogogo"},{"pid":"18d2d42c697bd9cf19c73fc5d123929e8a7a2eb3","tid":1148441,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"港樓 inevitable<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/mobile/000/029/442/cover_inevitable.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Fmobile%2F000%2F029%2F442%2Fcover_inevitable.jpg&h=679b9916&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac06b874aabab19714bcf6f582679a3cc394f357","tid":1148441,"uid":213824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:20:38.000Z","msg":"連登傻淡末日"},{"pid":"57495a73a0170dae5c64e583c24f6a508e0fb155","tid":1148441,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f670e05d3f51157e8c40407f8f3bdd2f260fa478","tid":1148441,"uid":103981,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:00:21.000Z","msg":"大灣區咁撚大，點解個個都要迫黎香港？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n陷家鏟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:29:16.000Z","msg":"深圳呢？又話龍頭？"},{"pid":"2116f563ba56e838a05029c380b851f50f8580b4","tid":1148441,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18d2d42c697bd9cf19c73fc5d123929e8a7a2eb3","tid":1148441,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:11:51.000Z","msg":"港樓 inevitable<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.kym-cdn.com/entries/icons/mobile/000/029/442/cover_inevitable.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.kym-cdn.com%2Fentries%2Ficons%2Fmobile%2F000%2F029%2F442%2Fcover_inevitable.jpg&h=679b9916&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"379df301ef5d633108290a5def9b2840bf6c5001","tid":1148441,"uid":62,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T05:47:41.000Z","msg":"政府：現時房屋供應緊張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6ee45f9dd2061081b334f953ec80e58e56cdf4","tid":1148441,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入市啦"},{"pid":"91b6430e549f39b5da13522be100226f29718169","tid":1148441,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"新香港人的購買力會填補人口老化所造成的住屋需求下降。<br />\n<br />\n。。。乜鬼野，佢地落黎係拎資源，又何來有購買力。。。"},{"pid":"06fdda7d1a1c6a7d43042352e61834afca85a221","tid":1148441,"uid":38550,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91b6430e549f39b5da13522be100226f29718169","tid":1148441,"uid":38962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:33:23.000Z","msg":"新香港人的購買力會填補人口老化所造成的住屋需求下降。<br />\n<br />\n。。。乜鬼野，佢地落黎係拎資源，又何來有購買力。。。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:52:39.000Z","msg":"殊途同歸<br />\n<br />\n有錢嗰班 嚟買炒樓 直接推高樓價<br />\n無錢嗰班 嚟攞公屋 調整公私房屋比例 私樓減少供應 間接推高樓價"},{"pid":"87b400e7133ea2299ea1aa39070d46752552d2a1","tid":1148441,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T09:55:46.000Z","msg":"唔係AA狗而係財演唱好之時...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8719829b77823d0034e1055f4d845c2709874c9a","tid":1148441,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:03:40.000Z","msg":"我想知廣東省除左極有錢人，有咩家庭可以比成至少四百幾萬港幣買層樓嚟投資/唔知做乜柒？"},{"pid":"de48861aa8a63065ac3071f24783e403ae61bd0c","tid":1148441,"uid":26770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"瑞銀不嬲係講反話幫客做操作<br />\n<br />\n當你個抄家條例過左<br />\n大陸人投資香港意慾一定細左"},{"pid":"6399a8afa03434d384f4f652d094e97e06ce2792","tid":1148441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T10:17:48.000Z","msg":"最後假升<br />\n<br />\n跟住 送終法 大跌90%"}]}